.DS_Store
.*.swp
# rig lease runtime state (the mutex + its audit log). Host-local, ephemeral,
# shared between agents via the filesystem — not git. The backlog itself
# (tickets/) IS git-tracked; only the live lease is ignored here.
.rig/
# jq writes tickets atomically via a .tmp sidecar; never commit a stray one.
tickets/*.tmp
.tmp/